aren't exactly young either.

292
00:20:12,086 --> 00:20:13,504
Why haven't they intervened?

293
00:20:15,464 --> 00:20:18,591
All the elders in their family
passed away early.

294
00:20:18,592 --> 00:20:21,094
They've had hard lives
since they were kids.

295
00:20:21,095 --> 00:20:23,138
They're still on welfare right now.

296
00:20:23,139 --> 00:20:24,931
They're busy trying
to get by each day,

297
00:20:24,932 --> 00:20:26,809
so they can't even dare to do this.

298
00:20:27,393 --> 00:20:29,186
You said they still live here, right?

299
00:20:30,646 --> 00:20:31,939
- The great-grandchildren?
- Yes.

300
00:20:32,523 --> 00:20:33,649
Can we meet them?

301
00:20:35,776 --> 00:20:37,277
There's one.

302
00:20:37,278 --> 00:20:38,362
Hey!

303
00:20:39,029 --> 00:20:40,823
- Hello!
- Hey!

304
00:20:42,366 --> 00:20:45,869
Thank you so much
for coming out here in person.

305
00:20:45,870 --> 00:20:47,620
Come now.

306
00:20:47,621 --> 00:20:51,624
I said you had to go and see it
for yourself to understand,

307
00:20:51,625 --> 00:20:52,835
so what could they do?

308
00:20:54,962 --> 00:20:57,798
I thought if I didn't settle this
before I die,

309
00:20:58,466 --> 00:20:59,841
I'd never be at peace.

310
00:20:59,842 --> 00:21:03,261
Goodness, you need to live a long life.
Don't say that, sir.

311
00:21:03,262 --> 00:21:06,598
If he weren't around in our town,
nothing would get done.

312
00:21:06,599 --> 00:21:07,975
Come on.

313
00:21:13,314 --> 00:21:15,356
Hurry and follow me. We're not done yet.

314
00:21:15,357 --> 00:21:16,442
Take care.

315
00:21:42,718 --> 00:21:43,843
Okay.

316
00:21:43,844 --> 00:21:46,679
Take this with you, okay?

