00:24:45,359 --> 00:24:46,735
Hi. What's up?

357
00:24:47,319 --> 00:24:49,029
Hey, Munjeong.

358
00:24:50,322 --> 00:24:54,159
Have you thought about
working in-house again by any chance?

359
00:24:54,743 --> 00:24:55,743
What?

360
00:24:55,744 --> 00:24:59,455
<i>It seemed like you were interested
in my company last time.</i>

361
00:24:59,456 --> 00:25:02,292
Well, there's an opening now,

