00:25:02,876 --> 00:25:04,795
<i>so I thought of you and called.</i>

363
00:25:05,504 --> 00:25:06,839
Really?

364
00:25:08,340 --> 00:25:10,843
<i>Maybe I read that wrong.</i>

365
00:25:11,468 --> 00:25:12,469
No, not at all.

366
00:25:13,053 --> 00:25:17,306
- Can I think it over and call you back?
<i>- Of course.</i>

367
00:25:17,307 --> 00:25:20,101
My gosh! You're going to get
your legs caught! Be careful!

368
00:25:20,102 --> 00:25:21,394
Sorry about that.

369
00:25:21,395 --> 00:25:25,106
Okay. So, the job posting will go up soon.

370
00:25:25,107 --> 00:25:29,027
I'll send you the details in advance.
