401
00:28:13,066 --> 00:28:14,650
- Could we take a photo?
- No.

402
00:28:14,651 --> 00:28:16,611
- We'd appreciate it.
- Please leave. You can't.

403
00:28:16,612 --> 00:28:17,779
No, just the contract...

404
00:28:19,448 --> 00:28:20,865
- The contract?
- Yes.

405
00:28:20,866 --> 00:28:22,742
There won't be any legal issues.

406
00:28:22,743 --> 00:28:24,786
We only need it as a reference.

407
00:28:27,915 --> 00:28:28,998
- All right, here.
- Thank you.

408
00:28:28,999 --> 00:28:31,042
If you get worried,
